   "source": [
    "## Final rule\n",
    "\n",
    "Model contract is used for hard gate.\n",
    "\n",
    "Evaluator-generated pass contract is forbidden.\n",
    "\n",
    "Natural language is recorded but does not decide hard veto.\n"
   ]
